  "title": "Operation Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Cargo/Parcel Tracking &amp; Monitoring</strong></p>\n<p>·        Track and trace shipments in real-time using logistics systems .</p>\n<p>·        Identify delays or exceptions (e.g., missed deliveries, damages) and escalate promptly.</p>\n<p><strong>Reporting &amp; Documentation</strong></p>\n<p>·        Generate and analyze daily, weekly, and monthly reports on shipment statuses, delays, and KPIs.</p>\n<p>·        Maintain accurate records of exceptions and resolutions.</p>\n<p><strong>Exception Case Management</strong></p>\n<p>·        Investigate and resolve delivery exceptions (e.g., rerouting, customer complaints).</p>\n<p>·        Coordinate with drivers, warehouses, and clients for timely follow-ups.</p>\n<p><strong>Ad-Hoc Support</strong></p>\n<p>·        Assist with urgent dispatch tasks, route adjustments, or administrative duties as needed.</p>",
